data.description: Don't miss your chance to own a beautifully restored historic home in the desirable Chicod school district of Pitt County! This charming 1910 residence has undergone a full transformation, blending classic character with modern convenience. Nestled on an expansive half-acre lot, this 3-bedroom plus bonus room, 2-bathroom home offers a spacious open-concept living area, luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main level, renovated bathrooms, an updated kitchen, a tankless water heater, and many other noteworthy upgrades. In 2016, this home underwent a comprehensive renovation, from the foundation to the roof, ensuring its enduring quality and charm. The entire home is powered by solar energy, saving you money! Step outside into your backyard oasis, complete with a 20x40 detached building that offers a perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of daily life. This versatile space is fully climate-controlled with AC, making it ideal for a home office, studio, or simply a relaxing getaway.  Experience the best of historic charm and modern living in this Pitt County gem. (Please do not access property without an appointment with a licensed real estate agent.)
